{"tid":1302649,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"毛主席：沒有調查就沒有發言權！","createTime":"2019-07-10T04:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T17:18:42.000Z","uid":262545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d1676faa0b97109fd64b295a807ace3fd11ecdc8","tid":1302649,"uid":262545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:25:34.000Z","msg":"簡介：<br />\n「沒有調查，沒有發言權」，是中國共產黨黨史上的80句口號之一。<br />\n<br />\n背景：<br />\n他指出：「你對某個問題沒有調查，就停止你對某個問題的發言權。」「注重調查！」「反對瞎說！」「中國革命鬥爭的勝利要靠中國同志瞭解中國情況」。「本本主義」者必須「速速改變保守思想！換取共產黨人的進步的鬥爭思想！到鬥爭中去！到群眾中作實際調查去！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你哋班政治中立嘅狗<br />\n乜柒嘢員佐級<br />\n奶共奶到咁出面<br />\n依家連主席嘅話都唔聽<br />\n冇調查仲有咩資格講咁多嘢啊<br />\n<br />\n應該快啲支持成立獨立調查委員會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"718b4ac143fa0afd8fba9d9236b072ec2787ee36","tid":1302649,"uid":262545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:27:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"122d43c92bbb922e388e12c4695c90c39c2d9fa8","tid":1302649,"uid":107216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:32:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c0331f4add46ff2108a645366a808abbfd043917","tid":1302649,"uid":80668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OGcuOeg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGcuOeg.png&h=8c22191f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c5c5697711b6a588f3c3bd42d142a28896fdcea","tid":1302649,"uid":262545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e277dfe9f481e3d30c16ed22a77f6193fae56aa6","tid":1302649,"uid":262545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:13:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5eb3aa195eecac4070ca349ff4aa7c96d7b026bc","tid":1302649,"uid":262545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:18: